National Pizza Co said it reached anagreement in principle to buy seven Straw Hat pizza restaurantsand certain related real estate for approximately three mlndlrs in cash.    The acquisitions will be converted to Pizza Hutrestaurants, said National Pizza, and are expected to generateannual sales of approximately eight mln dlrs.    When the sale is complete, it will bring to 24 the numberof restaurants operated by National Pizza, the company said. Reuter&#3;